FBIS4-9469 "dreeu080__a94038" FBIS-EEU-94-080-A Daily Report 26 April 1994 ANNEX Poland Pol Cancels Decision on Restructuring Pol Cancels Decision on Restructuring LD2604105494 Warsaw PAP in English 1022 GMT 26 Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY LD2604105494 Warsaw PAP English BFN [Text] Piotrkow Trybunalski, April 26 -- Industry Minister Marek Pol cancelled the controversial decision on mining industry restructuring as a result of negotiations with Solidarity leader Marian Krzaklewski that began earlier on Tuesday. Miners on strike promised to resume supplies of coal to power plants.
